    • relate

      public abstract boolean relate​(double t, double dt, CategorizedComponent arena, CategorizedComponent lifeCycle, CategorizedComponent group, CategorizedComponent focal, CategorizedComponent otherLifeCycle, CategorizedComponent otherGroup, CategorizedComponent other, DynamicSpace<SystemComponent> space)
      focal system component establishes a new relation to other system component. Notice that some parameters may be null when calling the method (as denoted by 'if any').
      Parameters:
      t - current time
      dt - current time step
      arena - the arena component, i.e. the top of the component hierarchy
      lifeCycle - the life cycle component of this focal component, if any
      group - the group component of this focal component, if any
      focal - the focal component (may be the arena, a group or lifecycle component)
      otherLifeCycle - the life cycle component of the other component, if any
      otherGroup - the group component of the other component, if any
      other - the other component (may be the arena, a group or lifecycle component)
      space - the space attached to the parent process, if any
      Returns:
